metadata.name: Atlantis-P Mistery Shell #1
metadata.description: Due to the call of the sea god Poseidon, Atlantis is about to rebirth in the Ethereum metaverse! To create the NFTs, we gathered 100+ well-known sorcerers and wizards from all over the world! 10000 NFT owners can become members of the future Atlantis Metaverse and enjoy various on-chain and off-chain privileges and discounts.
